    "prior-guided-llm-api-key-setup-wizard": {
      "id": "prior-guided-llm-api-key-setup-wizard",
      "name": "Guided LLM API key setup wizard",
      "content": "<ul><li><strong>Date completed:</strong> 2026-04-19</li><li><strong>Session duration:</strong> ~20 min</li><li><strong>Commit:</strong> <code>6275307</code></li><li><strong>Commits in cluster:</strong> 1</li><li><strong>Files changed:</strong> 1 (across cluster)</li><li><strong>Lines changed:</strong> +159 / -32 (across cluster)</li></ul><p>Step-by-step in-app instructions for obtaining and pasting an API key for each supported LLM provider, surfaced inside the Settings dialog so users can self-serve their own keys.</p>",
      "type": "document",
      "parentId": "month-2026-04",
      "childrenIds": [],
      "isExpanded": true,
      "prefix": "1"
    },
    "prior-llm-api-key-management-ui-settings-dialog-scrolling": {
      "id": "prior-llm-api-key-management-ui-settings-dialog-scrolling",
      "name": "LLM API key management UI + Settings dialog scrolling",
      "content": "<ul><li><strong>Date completed:</strong> 2026-04-19</li><li><strong>Session duration:</strong> not measured</li><li><strong>Commit:</strong> <code>3688849</code></li><li><strong>Commits in cluster:</strong> 1</li><li><strong>Files changed:</strong> 1 (across cluster)</li><li><strong>Lines changed:</strong> +112 / -1 (across cluster)</li></ul><p>Added a dedicated key-management section to the Settings dialog (paste, save, and reveal keys per provider) and fixed the dialog's broken scrolling behavior.</p>",
      "type": "document",
      "parentId": "month-2026-04",
      "childrenIds": [],
      "isExpanded": true,
      "prefix": "2"
    },
    "prior-second-brain-v1-reserved-outline-save-action-knowledge-chat-": {
      "id": "prior-second-brain-v1-reserved-outline-save-action-knowledge-chat-",
      "name": "Second Brain v1 - reserved outline + Save action + Knowledge Chat mode",
      "content": "<ul><li><strong>Date completed:</strong> 2026-04-19</li><li><strong>Session duration:</strong> ~1545 min</li><li><strong>Commit:</strong> <code>5f20e75</code></li><li><strong>Commits in cluster:</strong> 6</li><li><strong>Files changed:</strong> 14 (across cluster)</li><li><strong>Lines changed:</strong> +370 / -120 (across cluster)</li></ul><p>The original Second Brain feature: a reserved corpus outline, a Save action surfaced from any node, a Knowledge Chat mode that queries it, a dedicated Brain toolbar menu, an Unmerge restore step, and scoped collapse/expand keyboard shortcuts on the toggle button.</p>",
      "type": "document",
      "parentId": "month-2026-04",
      "childrenIds": [],
      "isExpanded": true,
      "prefix": "3"
    },
    "prior-secondbrainware-brand-rollout": {
      "id": "prior-secondbrainware-brand-rollout",
      "name": "SecondBrainWare brand rollout",
      "content": "<ul><li><strong>Date completed:</strong> 2026-04-18</li><li><strong>Session duration:</strong> not measured</li><li><strong>Commit:</strong> <code>f2069df</code></li><li><strong>Commits in cluster:</strong> 1</li><li><strong>Files changed:</strong> 6 (across cluster)</li><li><strong>Lines changed:</strong> +103 / -85 (across cluster)</li></ul><p>Updated the public-facing website and all in-app documentation strings to use the SecondBrainWare brand while keeping the internal IdiamPro codebase identifier intact.</p>",
      "type": "document",
      "parentId": "month-2026-04",
      "childrenIds": [],
      "isExpanded": true,
      "prefix": "4"
    },
    "prior-rename-generate-outline-to-generate-subtree-pre-fill-from-se": {
      "id": "prior-rename-generate-outline-to-generate-subtree-pre-fill-from-se",
      "name": "Rename Generate Outline to Generate Subtree, pre-fill from selected node",
      "content": "<ul><li><strong>Date completed:</strong> 2026-04-18</li><li><strong>Session duration:</strong> ~5 min</li><li><strong>Commit:</strong> <code>e015015</code></li><li><strong>Commits in cluster:</strong> 1</li><li><strong>Files changed:</strong> 4 (across cluster)</li><li><strong>Lines changed:</strong> +65 / -21 (across cluster)</li></ul><p>Renamed the AI flow that grows children under the selected node from 'Generate Outline' to 'Generate Subtree' and made it pre-fill the topic from the selected node so users don't have to retype.</p>",
      "type": "document",
      "parentId": "month-2026-04",
      "childrenIds": [],
      "isExpanded": true,
      "prefix": "5"
    },
    "prior-gemma-4-vision-describe-with-ai-button": {
      "id": "prior-gemma-4-vision-describe-with-ai-button",
      "name": "Gemma 4 vision + describe-with-AI button",
      "content": "<ul><li><strong>Date completed:</strong> 2026-04-17</li><li><strong>Session duration:</strong> not measured</li><li><strong>Commit:</strong> <code>d0d5588</code></li><li><strong>Commits in cluster:</strong> 1</li><li><strong>Files changed:</strong> 2 (across cluster)</li><li><strong>Lines changed:</strong> +158 / -15 (across cluster)</li></ul><p>Added local Gemma 4 vision support and a 'describe with AI' button so any image dropped into a node can be captioned locally without sending data off-device.</p>",
      "type": "document",
      "parentId": "month-2026-04",
      "childrenIds": [],
      "isExpanded": true,
      "prefix": "6"
    },
    "prior-ios-gesture-and-layout-bug-fixes-apr-15": {
      "id": "prior-ios-gesture-and-layout-bug-fixes-apr-15",
      "name": "iOS gesture and layout bug fixes (Apr 15)",
      "content": "<ul><li><strong>Date completed:</strong> 2026-04-15</li><li><strong>Session duration:</strong> ~75 min</li><li><strong>Commit:</strong> <code>0ace1ae</code></li><li><strong>Commits in cluster:</strong> 2</li><li><strong>Files changed:</strong> 5 (across cluster)</li><li><strong>Lines changed:</strong> +51 / -9 (across cluster)</li></ul><p>Three correctness fixes to iOS gesture handling and node-tree layout, plus disabling Gemma 4 thinking-mode preambles across all Ollama call paths so local AI responses don't leak chain-of-thought.</p>",
      "type": "document",
      "parentId": "month-2026-04",
      "childrenIds": [],
      "isExpanded": true,
      "prefix": "7"
    },
    "prior-migrate-local-ai-from-llama3-2-to-gemma-4": {
      "id": "prior-migrate-local-ai-from-llama3-2-to-gemma-4",
      "name": "Migrate local AI from llama3.2 to Gemma 4",
      "content": "<ul><li><strong>Date completed:</strong> 2026-04-10</li><li><strong>Session duration:</strong> ~715 min</li><li><strong>Commit:</strong> <code>3625bfc</code></li><li><strong>Commits in cluster:</strong> 1</li><li><strong>Files changed:</strong> 15 (across cluster)</li><li><strong>Lines changed:</strong> +947 / -115 (across cluster)</li></ul><p>Replaced the default local model with Gemma 4 across every Ollama call path, plus a dedicated Playwright smoke test that validates the model is reachable and answering.</p>",
      "type": "document",
      "parentId": "month-2026-04",
      "childrenIds": [],
      "isExpanded": true,
      "prefix": "8"
    },
    "prior-ai-image-descriptions-backup-restore-redesign-generate-menu-": {
      "id": "prior-ai-image-descriptions-backup-restore-redesign-generate-menu-",
      "name": "AI image descriptions, backup/restore redesign, Generate menu cleanup",
      "content": "<ul><li><strong>Date completed:</strong> 2026-04-03</li><li><strong>Session duration:</strong> ~60 min</li><li><strong>Commit:</strong> <code>1b3850d</code></li><li><strong>Commits in cluster:</strong> 1</li><li><strong>Files changed:</strong> 6 (across cluster)</li><li><strong>Lines changed:</strong> +189 / -71 (across cluster)</li></ul><p>Added AI-generated image descriptions inline in the content pane, redesigned the backup and restore flow with clearer affordances, and cleaned up the cluttered Generate menu structure.</p>",
      "type": "document",
      "parentId": "month-2026-04",
      "childrenIds": [],
      "isExpanded": true,
      "prefix": "9"
