    "prior-mcp-server-with-16-tools-auth-system": {
      "id": "prior-mcp-server-with-16-tools-auth-system",
      "name": "MCP server with 16 tools + auth system",
      "content": "<ul><li><strong>Date completed:</strong> 2026-04-03</li><li><strong>Session duration:</strong> not measured</li><li><strong>Commit:</strong> <code>42fdae0</code></li><li><strong>Commits in cluster:</strong> 1</li><li><strong>Files changed:</strong> 14 (across cluster)</li><li><strong>Lines changed:</strong> +3840 / -71 (across cluster)</li></ul><p>Shipped a full Model Context Protocol server exposing 16 tools (list outlines, read outline, create node, search, etc.) with an authentication system and onboarding documentation, so Claude Desktop/Code can drive IdiamPro programmatically.</p>",
      "type": "document",
      "parentId": "month-2026-04",
      "childrenIds": [],
