      "name": "Diagram type selector + cascading Escape + TestFlight macOS setup",
      "content": "<ul><li><strong>Date completed:</strong> 2026-04-03</li><li><strong>Session duration:</strong> not measured</li><li><strong>Commit:</strong> <code>791e5b4</code></li><li><strong>Commits in cluster:</strong> 1</li><li><strong>Files changed:</strong> 24 (across cluster)</li><li><strong>Lines changed:</strong> +339 / -116 (across cluster)</li></ul><p>Added a diagram type selector to the Mermaid editor (flowchart, sequence, class, etc.), made Escape cascade out of nested dialogs/editors correctly, fixed several colour issues, and set up the TestFlight macOS build pipeline.</p>",
