    "prior-light-dark-theme-toggle": {
      "id": "prior-light-dark-theme-toggle",
      "name": "Light/dark theme toggle",
      "content": "<ul><li><strong>Date completed:</strong> 2026-03-26</li><li><strong>Session duration:</strong> not measured</li><li><strong>Commit:</strong> <code>cb9a677</code></li><li><strong>Commits in cluster:</strong> 1</li><li><strong>Files changed:</strong> 9 (across cluster)</li><li><strong>Lines changed:</strong> +204 / -1139 (across cluster)</li></ul><p>Added a light/dark theme toggle and updated every in-app icon colour to render correctly in both modes.</p>",
