    "prior-search-filters-consent-decline-warning-auto-devtools-off": {
      "id": "prior-search-filters-consent-decline-warning-auto-devtools-off",
      "name": "Search filters + consent decline warning + auto-DevTools off",
      "content": "<ul><li><strong>Date completed:</strong> 2026-03-23</li><li><strong>Session duration:</strong> not measured</li><li><strong>Commit:</strong> <code>1c31881</code></li><li><strong>Commits in cluster:</strong> 2</li><li><strong>Files changed:</strong> 13 (across cluster)</li><li><strong>Lines changed:</strong> +2044 / -167 (across cluster)</li></ul><p>Added category filters to the search dialog (search names only, content only, etc.), a warning when a user declines AI consent so they understand what gets disabled, and stopped Electron from auto-opening DevTools on every launch.</p>",
      "type": "document",
      "parentId": "month-2026-03",
