    "prior-external-modification-polling-fn-key-dictation-fix-session-a": {
      "id": "prior-external-modification-polling-fn-key-dictation-fix-session-a",
      "name": "External modification polling + Fn-key dictation fix + session actions log",
      "content": "<ul><li><strong>Date completed:</strong> 2026-03-23</li><li><strong>Session duration:</strong> not measured</li><li><strong>Commit:</strong> <code>4c1e039</code></li><li><strong>Commits in cluster:</strong> 1</li><li><strong>Files changed:</strong> 1 (across cluster)</li><li><strong>Lines changed:</strong> +9 / -0 (across cluster)</li></ul><p>Added periodic polling for outline files modified outside the app (so MCP edits and other tools surface immediately), a fix for the Fn-key dictation toggle on macOS, and a Session Actions Log section in the Bootstrap Plan outline for PM tracking.</p>",
      "type": "document",
      "parentId": "month-2026-03",
      "childrenIds": [],
      "isExpanded": true,
      "prefix": "3"
    },
    "prior-ai-consent-dialog-privacy-policy-external-modification-polli": {
      "id": "prior-ai-consent-dialog-privacy-policy-external-modification-polli",
      "name": "AI consent dialog + privacy policy + external modification polling",
      "content": "<ul><li><strong>Date completed:</strong> 2026-03-23</li><li><strong>Session duration:</strong> not measured</li><li><strong>Commit:</strong> <code>4a805e1</code></li><li><strong>Commits in cluster:</strong> 1</li><li><strong>Files changed:</strong> 11 (across cluster)</li><li><strong>Lines changed:</strong> +631 / -82 (across cluster)</li></ul><p>Added a first-launch AI consent dialog with a written privacy policy and the initial external-modification detection plumbing so files edited outside the app are reloaded.</p>",
      "type": "document",
      "parentId": "month-2026-03",
      "childrenIds": [],
      "isExpanded": true,
      "prefix": "4"
    },
    "prior-podcast-editing-studio-tone-level-controls-30-export-formats": {
      "id": "prior-podcast-editing-studio-tone-level-controls-30-export-formats",
      "name": "Podcast editing studio + tone/level controls + 30+ export formats + killer features list",
      "content": "<ul><li><strong>Date completed:</strong> 2026-03-12</li><li><strong>Session duration:</strong> not measured</li><li><strong>Commit:</strong> <code>b3c550d</code></li><li><strong>Commits in cluster:</strong> 1</li><li><strong>Files changed:</strong> 52 (across cluster)</li><li><strong>Lines changed:</strong> +4110 / -412 (across cluster)</li></ul><p>Major shipment: an in-app podcast editing studio (trim, reorder, regenerate segments), tone and level controls for AI generation, expansion of the export system to 30+ formats, and a curated killer-features outline for marketing.</p>",
      "type": "document",
      "parentId": "month-2026-03",
      "childrenIds": [],
      "isExpanded": true,
