      "name": "Website Generation guide + auto-restart instruction",
      "content": "<ul><li><strong>Date completed:</strong> 2026-03-02</li><li><strong>Session duration:</strong> not measured</li><li><strong>Commit:</strong> <code>a814782</code></li><li><strong>Commits in cluster:</strong> 1</li><li><strong>Files changed:</strong> 5 (across cluster)</li><li><strong>Lines changed:</strong> +35 / -4 (across cluster)</li></ul><p>Added an in-app guide for the website generation feature plus the auto-restart behavior wired into Electron so code changes don't require manual restarts during development.</p>",
