    "prior-website-export-multi-template-gallery-customization-wizard": {
      "id": "prior-website-export-multi-template-gallery-customization-wizard",
      "name": "Website export + multi-template gallery + customization wizard",
      "content": "<ul><li><strong>Date completed:</strong> 2026-02-28</li><li><strong>Session duration:</strong> not measured</li><li><strong>Commit:</strong> <code>7e5906d</code></li><li><strong>Commits in cluster:</strong> 8</li><li><strong>Files changed:</strong> 78 (across cluster)</li><li><strong>Lines changed:</strong> +23492 / -5713 (across cluster)</li></ul><p>Shipped the full website-export feature: convert any outline into a publishable static site using one of 8 best-in-class templates, with an interactive preview carousel, an outline-view toggle in the preview, a customization wizard for colors/fonts/layout, and a consolidated Share toolbar entry.</p>",
      "type": "document",
      "parentId": "month-2026-02",
      "childrenIds": [],
      "isExpanded": true,
      "prefix": "1"
    },
    "prior-playwright-electron-test-automation-welcome-tour-4-tier-subs": {
      "id": "prior-playwright-electron-test-automation-welcome-tour-4-tier-subs",
      "name": "Playwright Electron test automation + Welcome Tour + 4-tier subscription plans",
      "content": "<ul><li><strong>Date completed:</strong> 2026-02-12</li><li><strong>Session duration:</strong> not measured</li><li><strong>Commit:</strong> <code>59ae19b</code></li><li><strong>Commits in cluster:</strong> 3</li><li><strong>Files changed:</strong> 34 (across cluster)</li><li><strong>Lines changed:</strong> +13533 / -168 (across cluster)</li></ul><p>Built the Playwright-based Electron test harness with structured reporting (used today by 'TEST EVERYTHING'), added an in-app Welcome Tour for new users, shipped the 4-tier subscription plan structure (Free/Standard/Premium/Pro), and added the docs/outlines version-control sync.</p>",
      "type": "document",
      "parentId": "month-2026-02",
      "childrenIds": [],
      "isExpanded": true,
      "prefix": "2"
    },
    "prior-1-000-000-node-stress-test-test-your-system-cta": {
      "id": "prior-1-000-000-node-stress-test-test-your-system-cta",
      "name": "1,000,000+ node stress test + Test Your System CTA",
      "content": "<ul><li><strong>Date completed:</strong> 2026-02-11</li><li><strong>Session duration:</strong> not measured</li><li><strong>Commit:</strong> <code>5aeed40</code></li><li><strong>Commits in cluster:</strong> 3</li><li><strong>Files changed:</strong> 6 (across cluster)</li><li><strong>Lines changed:</strong> +452 / -23 (across cluster)</li></ul><p>Extended the in-app stress test to 1,000,000 nodes (up from 500,000), updated marketing copy to advertise the million-node capacity, added a 'Test Your System' button linking to the stress-test page, and fixed hydration mismatches in the stress-test and particles-background pages.</p>",
      "type": "document",
      "parentId": "month-2026-02",
      "childrenIds": [],
      "isExpanded": true,
      "prefix": "3"
    },
    "prior-clickable-links-in-content-editor": {
      "id": "prior-clickable-links-in-content-editor",
      "name": "Clickable links in content editor",
      "content": "<ul><li><strong>Date completed:</strong> 2026-02-11</li><li><strong>Session duration:</strong> not measured</li><li><strong>Commit:</strong> <code>02cf6d1</code></li><li><strong>Commits in cluster:</strong> 1</li><li><strong>Files changed:</strong> 1 (across cluster)</li><li><strong>Lines changed:</strong> +2 / -1 (across cluster)</li></ul><p>Enabled clickable hyperlinks inside the rich-text content editor so users can navigate URLs without copying them out.</p>",
      "type": "document",
      "parentId": "month-2026-02",
      "childrenIds": [],
      "isExpanded": true,
      "prefix": "4"
    },
    "prior-marketing-site-redesign-intelligence-amplifier-positioning-r": {
      "id": "prior-marketing-site-redesign-intelligence-amplifier-positioning-r",
      "name": "Marketing site redesign + Intelligence Amplifier positioning + restructured routes",
      "content": "<ul><li><strong>Date completed:</strong> 2026-02-10</li><li><strong>Session duration:</strong> not measured</li><li><strong>Commit:</strong> <code>7fbbc94</code></li><li><strong>Commits in cluster:</strong> 4</li><li><strong>Files changed:</strong> 10 (across cluster)</li><li><strong>Lines changed:</strong> +4903 / -61 (across cluster)</li></ul><p>Rebuilt the marketing landing page for professional researchers with a demo video, case studies, comparison table, academic pricing tier, and Intelligence Amplifier / Second Brain positioning. Restructured app routes into marketing home, dedicated app page, and dedicated beta page.</p>",
      "type": "document",
      "parentId": "month-2026-02",
      "childrenIds": [],
      "isExpanded": true,
      "prefix": "5"
    },
    "prior-unified-multi-format-import-export-system": {
      "id": "prior-unified-multi-format-import-export-system",
      "name": "Unified multi-format import/export system",
      "content": "<ul><li><strong>Date completed:</strong> 2026-02-10</li><li><strong>Session duration:</strong> not measured</li><li><strong>Commit:</strong> <code>ba4dafb</code></li><li><strong>Commits in cluster:</strong> 3</li><li><strong>Files changed:</strong> 24 (across cluster)</li><li><strong>Lines changed:</strong> +3145 / -85 (across cluster)</li></ul><p>Shipped a unified import/export pipeline with multi-format support (OPML, Markdown, JSON, plain text, OmniOutliner OPML, MindNode, Workflowy, etc.) plus a single Import dialog that auto-detects file type and a single Export dialog that lets users pick any format.</p>",
      "type": "document",
      "parentId": "month-2026-02",
      "childrenIds": [],
      "isExpanded": true,
      "prefix": "6"
    },
    "prior-ai-reasoning-depth-setting-quick-standard-deep-ai-menu-conso": {
      "id": "prior-ai-reasoning-depth-setting-quick-standard-deep-ai-menu-conso",
      "name": "AI Reasoning Depth setting (Quick/Standard/Deep) + AI menu consolidation",
      "content": "<ul><li><strong>Date completed:</strong> 2026-02-07</li><li><strong>Session duration:</strong> not measured</li><li><strong>Commit:</strong> <code>7613ce4</code></li><li><strong>Commits in cluster:</strong> 5</li><li><strong>Files changed:</strong> 17 (across cluster)</li><li><strong>Lines changed:</strong> +330 / -148 (across cluster)</li></ul><p>Added the AI Reasoning Depth setting (Quick / Standard / Deep) wired into Research & Import and Knowledge Chat, consolidated every AI feature into a single AI Menu, combined Research & Import and Knowledge Chat into one AI Tools dropdown, and moved subscription management from the AI menu to Settings > Account.</p>",
      "type": "document",
      "parentId": "month-2026-02",
      "childrenIds": [],
      "isExpanded": true,
      "prefix": "7"
    },
    "prior-short-timestamp-format-m-d-yy": {
      "id": "prior-short-timestamp-format-m-d-yy",
      "name": "Short timestamp format (M/D/YY)",
      "content": "<ul><li><strong>Date completed:</strong> 2026-02-07</li><li><strong>Session duration:</strong> not measured</li><li><strong>Commit:</strong> <code>052371f</code></li><li><strong>Commits in cluster:</strong> 1</li><li><strong>Files changed:</strong> 2 (across cluster)</li><li><strong>Lines changed:</strong> +11 / -14 (across cluster)</li></ul><p>Changed the timestamp display format across the app to short M/D/YY style (e.g., 2/7/26) so date columns stay compact.</p>",
      "type": "document",
      "parentId": "month-2026-02",
      "childrenIds": [],
      "isExpanded": true,
      "prefix": "8"
    },
    "prior-unmerge-toolbar-button-for-research-import": {
      "id": "prior-unmerge-toolbar-button-for-research-import",
      "name": "Unmerge toolbar button for Research & Import",
      "content": "<ul><li><strong>Date completed:</strong> 2026-02-07</li><li><strong>Session duration:</strong> not measured</li><li><strong>Commit:</strong> <code>f970fa0</code></li><li><strong>Commits in cluster:</strong> 3</li><li><strong>Files changed:</strong> 17 (across cluster)</li><li><strong>Lines changed:</strong> +337 / -32 (across cluster)</li></ul><p>Added an Unmerge button to the toolbar (and the corresponding Undo Merge action) for Research & Import, persisting the unmerge backup to disk so it survives app restarts.</p>",
      "type": "document",
      "parentId": "month-2026-02",
      "childrenIds": [],
      "isExpanded": true,
      "prefix": "9"
    },
    "prior-search-auto-expand-app-launch-fix-delete-shortcut": {
      "id": "prior-search-auto-expand-app-launch-fix-delete-shortcut",
      "name": "Search auto-expand + app launch fix + Delete shortcut",
      "content": "<ul><li><strong>Date completed:</strong> 2026-02-07</li><li><strong>Session duration:</strong> not measured</li><li><strong>Commit:</strong> <code>bfd9ed4</code></li><li><strong>Commits in cluster:</strong> 1</li><li><strong>Files changed:</strong> 5 (across cluster)</li><li><strong>Lines changed:</strong> +91 / -79 (across cluster)</li></ul><p>Search results now auto-expand collapsed ancestors so matched nodes are visible, fixed a launch race that left the app blank on cold start, and added Delete-key keyboard shortcut to remove the selected node.</p>",
      "type": "document",
      "parentId": "month-2026-02",
      "childrenIds": [],
      "isExpanded": true,
      "prefix": "10"
    },
    "prior-pdf-import-dialog-audio-player-window-drag-region": {
      "id": "prior-pdf-import-dialog-audio-player-window-drag-region",
      "name": "PDF import dialog + audio player + window drag region",
      "content": "<ul><li><strong>Date completed:</strong> 2026-02-04</li><li><strong>Session duration:</strong> not measured</li><li><strong>Commit:</strong> <code>b0ea4e1</code></li><li><strong>Commits in cluster:</strong> 6</li><li><strong>Files changed:</strong> 21 (across cluster)</li><li><strong>Lines changed:</strong> +474 / -147 (across cluster)</li></ul><p>Added a dedicated PDF import dialog with AI text formatting, an inline audio player for media nodes, a custom Electron window drag region, an Insert App / Insert File button pair (LayoutGrid + AppWindow icons), and a unified 'Import File' action that auto-detects file type.</p>",
      "type": "document",
      "parentId": "month-2026-02",
      "childrenIds": [],
      "isExpanded": true,
      "prefix": "11"
    },
    "prior-generate-podcast-feature-subtree-to-conversational-audio": {
      "id": "prior-generate-podcast-feature-subtree-to-conversational-audio",
      "name": "Generate Podcast feature - subtree to conversational audio",
      "content": "<ul><li><strong>Date completed:</strong> 2026-02-03</li><li><strong>Session duration:</strong> not measured</li><li><strong>Commit:</strong> <code>e834cfd</code></li><li><strong>Commits in cluster:</strong> 5</li><li><strong>Files changed:</strong> 18 (across cluster)</li><li><strong>Lines changed:</strong> +1220 / -106 (across cluster)</li></ul><p>Shipped Generate Podcast: select any subtree and convert it into a NotebookLM-style conversational audio file, with persisted style/voice/length/model preferences, in-browser MP3 playback, and a pending-import recovery dialog if generation is interrupted.</p>",
      "type": "document",
      "parentId": "month-2026-02",
      "childrenIds": [],
      "isExpanded": true,
      "prefix": "12"
    },
    "prior-enter-creates-sibling-double-click-edits-name-swap": {
      "id": "prior-enter-creates-sibling-double-click-edits-name-swap",
      "name": "Enter creates sibling, double-click edits name (swap)",
      "content": "<ul><li><strong>Date completed:</strong> 2026-02-03</li><li><strong>Session duration:</strong> not measured</li><li><strong>Commit:</strong> <code>151dac4</code></li><li><strong>Commits in cluster:</strong> 1</li><li><strong>Files changed:</strong> 6 (across cluster)</li><li><strong>Lines changed:</strong> +13 / -13 (across cluster)</li></ul><p>Swapped two of the most-used keyboard behaviors so Enter now creates a sibling node (instead of editing) and double-click enters edit mode (instead of creating a child). Matches industry-standard outliner expectations.</p>",
      "type": "document",
      "parentId": "month-2026-02",
      "childrenIds": [],
      "isExpanded": true,
      "prefix": "13"
    },
    "prior-clipboard-paste-drag-drop-for-images-and-media": {
      "id": "prior-clipboard-paste-drag-drop-for-images-and-media",
      "name": "Clipboard paste + drag-drop for images and media",
      "content": "<ul><li><strong>Date completed:</strong> 2026-02-02</li><li><strong>Session duration:</strong> not measured</li><li><strong>Commit:</strong> <code>28cae6b</code></li><li><strong>Commits in cluster:</strong> 3</li><li><strong>Files changed:</strong> 6 (across cluster)</li><li><strong>Lines changed:</strong> +127 / -24 (across cluster)</li></ul><p>Added clipboard image paste, generalized the paste and drag-drop handlers to accept every media type, and made HTML pasted from Apple Notes / web pages bring its embedded images along.</p>",
      "type": "document",
      "parentId": "month-2026-02",
      "childrenIds": [],
      "isExpanded": true,
      "prefix": "14"
    },
