      "id": "prior-multi-select-sources-knowledge-chat-improvements-security-ha",
      "name": "Multi-select sources + Knowledge Chat improvements + security hardening",
      "content": "<ul><li><strong>Date completed:</strong> 2026-02-01</li><li><strong>Session duration:</strong> not measured</li><li><strong>Commit:</strong> <code>4039364</code></li><li><strong>Commits in cluster:</strong> 1</li><li><strong>Files changed:</strong> 23 (across cluster)</li><li><strong>Lines changed:</strong> +3944 / -889 (across cluster)</li></ul><p>Accumulated feature work: multi-select sources in Research & Import, Knowledge Chat UX improvements, security fixes, and added test coverage.</p>",
