    "prior-knowledge-chat-with-superoutline-sync-ollama-fallback": {
      "id": "prior-knowledge-chat-with-superoutline-sync-ollama-fallback",
      "name": "Knowledge Chat with superoutline sync + Ollama fallback",
      "content": "<ul><li><strong>Date completed:</strong> 2026-01-31</li><li><strong>Session duration:</strong> not measured</li><li><strong>Commit:</strong> <code>4bf30db</code></li><li><strong>Commits in cluster:</strong> 6</li><li><strong>Files changed:</strong> 19 (across cluster)</li><li><strong>Lines changed:</strong> +941 / -52 (across cluster)</li></ul><p>Shipped Knowledge Chat: an AI search/Q&A mode that indexes the user's entire outline corpus into a superoutline, queries it with Gemini, and falls back to Ollama if the API call fails. Includes provider labeling, double-click and dark-mode fixes, and graceful handling of Ollama status check failures.</p>",
      "type": "document",
      "parentId": "month-2026-01",
      "childrenIds": [],
      "isExpanded": true,
      "prefix": "1"
    },
    "prior-automatic-backup-system-for-outline-files": {
      "id": "prior-automatic-backup-system-for-outline-files",
      "name": "Automatic backup system for outline files",
      "content": "<ul><li><strong>Date completed:</strong> 2026-01-31</li><li><strong>Session duration:</strong> not measured</li><li><strong>Commit:</strong> <code>acf9cf8</code></li><li><strong>Commits in cluster:</strong> 1</li><li><strong>Files changed:</strong> 4 (across cluster)</li><li><strong>Lines changed:</strong> +64 / -1 (across cluster)</li></ul><p>Added an automatic backup system that snapshots every .idm file on save with rolling history so users can recover from accidental edits or corruption.</p>",
      "type": "document",
      "parentId": "month-2026-01",
      "childrenIds": [],
      "isExpanded": true,
      "prefix": "2"
    },
    "prior-large-outline-performance-ios-improvements-auto-save-checkbo": {
      "id": "prior-large-outline-performance-ios-improvements-auto-save-checkbo",
      "name": "Large outline performance + iOS improvements + auto-save + checkbox lists",
      "content": "<ul><li><strong>Date completed:</strong> 2026-01-29</li><li><strong>Session duration:</strong> not measured</li><li><strong>Commit:</strong> <code>b7dfa9c</code></li><li><strong>Commits in cluster:</strong> 3</li><li><strong>Files changed:</strong> 28 (across cluster)</li><li><strong>Lines changed:</strong> +2144 / -291 (across cluster)</li></ul><p>Performance overhaul for very large outlines, a batch of iOS polish, the dirty-flag auto-save system, mtime-based external-change detection, and rich checkbox-list support inside content nodes.</p>",
      "type": "document",
      "parentId": "month-2026-01",
      "childrenIds": [],
      "isExpanded": true,
      "prefix": "3"
    },
    "prior-two-pass-organization-for-book-length-imports-chunked-extrac": {
      "id": "prior-two-pass-organization-for-book-length-imports-chunked-extrac",
      "name": "Two-pass organization for book-length imports + chunked extraction",
      "content": "<ul><li><strong>Date completed:</strong> 2026-01-25</li><li><strong>Session duration:</strong> not measured</li><li><strong>Commit:</strong> <code>d4e1a6c</code></li><li><strong>Commits in cluster:</strong> 4</li><li><strong>Files changed:</strong> 22 (across cluster)</li><li><strong>Lines changed:</strong> +2470 / -595 (across cluster)</li></ul><p>Major Research & Import upgrade: two-pass AI organization for book-length sources, chunked extraction so massive PDFs/EPUBs no longer timeout, dynamic chapter limits based on content complexity, content-first bullet-based output, rate-limit protection, and overall UX polish.</p>",
      "type": "document",
      "parentId": "month-2026-01",
      "childrenIds": [],
      "isExpanded": true,
      "prefix": "4"
    },
    "prior-sidebar-multi-select-context-menu-arrow-key-navigation": {
      "id": "prior-sidebar-multi-select-context-menu-arrow-key-navigation",
      "name": "Sidebar multi-select + context menu + arrow key navigation",
      "content": "<ul><li><strong>Date completed:</strong> 2026-01-25</li><li><strong>Session duration:</strong> not measured</li><li><strong>Commit:</strong> <code>5f1aa46</code></li><li><strong>Commits in cluster:</strong> 1</li><li><strong>Files changed:</strong> 3 (across cluster)</li><li><strong>Lines changed:</strong> +318 / -58 (across cluster)</li></ul><p>Added multi-select with Shift/Cmd click in the outline sidebar, a right-click context menu, and full arrow-key navigation so users can drive the sidebar entirely from the keyboard.</p>",
      "type": "document",
      "parentId": "month-2026-01",
      "childrenIds": [],
      "isExpanded": true,
      "prefix": "5"
    },
    "prior-google-picker-dialogs-for-docs-sheets-slides-maps-excalidraw": {
      "id": "prior-google-picker-dialogs-for-docs-sheets-slides-maps-excalidraw",
      "name": "Google picker dialogs for Docs, Sheets, Slides, Maps + Excalidraw",
      "content": "<ul><li><strong>Date completed:</strong> 2026-01-22</li><li><strong>Session duration:</strong> not measured</li><li><strong>Commit:</strong> <code>0542ff7</code></li><li><strong>Commits in cluster:</strong> 1</li><li><strong>Files changed:</strong> 5 (across cluster)</li><li><strong>Lines changed:</strong> +653 / -15 (across cluster)</li></ul><p>Added Google picker dialogs for inserting Docs, Sheets, Slides, and Maps embeds; replaced tldraw with the MIT-licensed Excalidraw for drawing nodes; fixed Excalidraw canvas persistence and routed picker dialogs through the system browser.</p>",
      "type": "document",
      "parentId": "month-2026-01",
      "childrenIds": [],
      "isExpanded": true,
      "prefix": "6"
    },
    "prior-photo-video-image-import-fullscreen-view-youtube-picker": {
      "id": "prior-photo-video-image-import-fullscreen-view-youtube-picker",
      "name": "Photo / video / image import + fullscreen view + YouTube picker",
      "content": "<ul><li><strong>Date completed:</strong> 2026-01-19</li><li><strong>Session duration:</strong> not measured</li><li><strong>Commit:</strong> <code>e573a36</code></li><li><strong>Commits in cluster:</strong> 2</li><li><strong>Files changed:</strong> 5 (across cluster)</li><li><strong>Lines changed:</strong> +305 / -7 (across cluster)</li></ul><p>Added photo, video, and image import to the content pane with persistent embedding even for large files, plus a fullscreen view for media and a YouTube picker dialog with a browser-based selection workflow.</p>",
      "type": "document",
      "parentId": "month-2026-01",
      "childrenIds": [],
